<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3155601" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="3">Once you convert a line or a text object to a contour, you can no longer edit it as you normally would. Instead, you can edit the contour as you would any polygon, including using the <emph>Edit â€“ Points </emph>command to adjust its shape.</paragraph>
